Interestingly, I also took &lt;a href=&#34;https://cs87-dartmouth.github.io/Fall2022/darts-overview.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Prof. Wojciech Jarosz&amp;rsquo;s rendering algorithms&lt;/a&gt; in FA22 and they are somewhat complementary to each other.
